aces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過開始就建議11甚至10開始"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T00:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:52:17.000Z","msg":"明明Amy Pond, Rory 先最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ceb1b619a76b07fae1e0546528b9bda27dc19b","tid":2194922,"uid":366741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:11:43.000Z","msg":"season 5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92bd4a23b0c8bf9675547abb7970395eadf90af","tid":2194922,"uid":277992,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:03:10.000Z","msg":"9-11doctor<br />\n<br />\n之後無咩心機再追落去"},{"pid":"220141a51b733510e1b0a1bfcce3168b8a7edada","tid":2194922,"uid":251793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:22:51.000Z","msg":"David Tennant 同 Billie Piper 果段最感人"},{"pid":"cd2cf6e8ad12c7fa57034715e3d5929561ff4f51","tid":2194922,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"220141a51b733510e1b0a1bfcce3168b8a7edada","tid":2194922,"uid":251793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:22:51.000Z","msg":"David Tennant 同 Billie Piper 果段最感人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"David Tennant<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74167110c0fa0bbd30be120a7c993ded4b50dee2","tid":2194922,"uid":121275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:52:41.000Z","msg":"由2005開始睇啦，之後就會想睇返1963<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得睇埋Torchwood, Sarah Jane Adventure同Class<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw啲fans唔會叫Dr Who, 一定係Doctor Who:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbcamerica.com/anglophenia/2012/10/doctor-whom-five-common-points-of-time-lord-pedantry\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbcamerica.com%2Fanglophenia%2F2012%2F10%2Fdoctor-whom-five-common-points-of-time-lord-pedantry&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=70d053f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbcamerica.com/anglophenia/2012/10/doctor-whom-five-common-points-of-time-lord-pedantry</a><br />\n<br />\nRule 1: It&rsquo;s not Dr Who, ever.<br />\nIt&rsquo;s a common thing, when referring to a properly qualified doctor by name, to contract the title down to Dr. especially when addressing letters. This is, ironically, to do with issues of both time (it takes longer to write &ldquo;octo&rdquo; in the middle) and space (some envelopes are really tiny). However, while being superbly qualified in all sorts of scientific disciplines, the Doctor in Doctor Who is not an actual Doctor. He is called the Doctor: he&rsquo;s not Doctor the Doctor. If he was, you&rsquo;d be fine to start your letters &ldquo;Dear Dr. the Doctor,&rdquo; but as he isn&rsquo;t, and we don&rsquo;t know his surname (see Rule 2) you can&rsquo;t write Dr. Who, or Dr Who."},{"pid":"37218d959fc870a74d95500a686283ac0df44f21","tid":2194922,"uid":334758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:56:48.000Z","msg":"由第9任doctor開始睇 Fantastic!"},{"pid":"815026c2e89239697e7f3c3f56d8d45c1a466cc9","tid":2194922,"uid":175032,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"74167110c0fa0bbd30be120a7c993ded4b50dee2","tid":2194922,"uid":121275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:52:41.000Z","msg":"由2005開始睇啦，之後就會想睇返1963<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得睇埋Torchwood, Sarah Jane Adventure同Class<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw啲fans唔會叫Dr Who, 一定係Doctor Who:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbcamerica.com/anglophenia/2012/10/doctor-whom-five-common-points-of-time-lord-pedantry\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbcamerica.com%2Fanglophenia%2F2012%2F10%2Fdoctor-whom-five-common-points-of-time-lord-pedantry&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=70d053f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbcamerica.com/anglophenia/2012/10/doctor-whom-five-common-points-of-time-lord-pedantry</a><br />\n<br />\nRule 1: It&rsquo;s not Dr Who, ever.<br />\nIt&rsquo;s a common thing, when referring to a properly qualified doctor by name, to contract the title down to Dr. especially when addressing letters. This is, ironically, to do with issues of both time (it takes longer to write &ldquo;octo&rdquo; in the middle) and space (some envelopes are really tiny). However, while being superbly qualified in all sorts of scientific disciplines, the Doctor in Doctor Who is not an actual Doctor. He is called the Doctor: he&rsquo;s not Doctor the Doctor. If he was, you&rsquo;d be fine to start your letters &ldquo;Dear Dr. the Doctor,&rdquo; but as he isn&rsquo;t, and we don&rsquo;t know his surname (see Rule 2) you can&rsquo;t write Dr. Who, or Dr Who."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:58:16.000Z","msg":"我未係fan<br />\n唔曉你地原來有rule<br />\n多謝分享"},{"pid":"f33d3e11869617bdbaf490454df606118d51343f","tid":2194922,"uid":67186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:00:50.000Z","msg":"舊版4th doctor?"},{"pid":"2c533466f05c10ac1616f7ebdf5c40ecb326d85a","tid":2194922,"uid":37885,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T16:24:04.000Z","msg":"2005年series 1 第9任doctor(新版)開始睇好啲<br />\n1963-1989嘅season1-26(舊版第1-7任)同埋電影版(第8任)就有興趣先睇, 因為太舊, 拍攝手法同節奏未必啱依家口味<br />\n<br />\n好多人都係series 1入坑, 咁個大主線劇情會比較完整啲<br />\n<br />\n利申：最愛11任"},{"pid":"2f10cf8864245d5421c264c2f26ccc5749aff5b0","tid":2194922,"uid":32089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T16:30:24.000Z","msg":"由九叔開始睇啦<br />\n10仔同11仔都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇埋12叔就可以唔洗再睇落去<br />\n唔想睇13姨"},{"pid":"8111e878e507de90d02668424693261898d5bfa4","tid":2194922,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T19:31:24.000Z","msg":"我個人推薦睇10先<br />\n<br />\n9 係新DW 入面最舊嘅<br />\n啲CG化妝比較原始，同埋得一季<br />\n雖然劇情同10係連住，但係唔睇住影響都唔太大<br />\n<br />\n10 多季啲<br />\n比較偏向單元劇，條主線冇咁重<br />\n<br />\n11 就複雜啲<br />\n啲時間線比較 wibbly-wobbly,&nbsp;timey-wimey<br />\n除非你本身睇好多玩時間嘅科幻野<br />\n唔係有啲難跟<br />\n<br />\n12 都好睇，有Clara<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇你接唔接受到主角係阿叔<br />\n12叔啲speech都好正"},{"pid":"d852de6ea2962e48737f89beee1e83fd53953b07","tid":2194922,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T19:41:28.000Z","msg":"David Tennant同Matt Smith最正<br />\nKaren Gillan<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65dc4258f88cd8fea666483d758f1aeb471432af","tid":2194922,"uid":75448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c533466f05c10ac1616f7ebdf5c40ecb326d85a","tid":2194922,"uid":37885,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T16:24:04.000Z","msg":"2005年series 1 第9任doctor(新版)開始睇好啲<br />\n1963-1989嘅season1-26(舊版第1-7任)同埋電影版(第8任)就有興趣先睇, 因為太舊, 拍攝手法同節奏未必啱依家口味<br />\n<br />\n好多人都係series 1入坑, 咁個大主線劇情會比較完整啲<br />\n<br />\n利申：最愛11任"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T19:44:59.000Z","msg":"當年atv 國際台播先接觸到，最記得個女人條眉好粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}